  <lyrics>[V1]
 /Kay jallp’api kaspa, llakiyilapi purini./
 Ay, Dioslla kusichiwan Payman qayllajtíy./
 
[V2]
 Oqharillawayña janaj pacha llajtaman./
 Ay, /wiñay kawsayniyta qopuwankiña./
 
[V3]
 /Pusarillawayña kallpaykita qowaspa./
 Ay, /wiñay kawsayniyta Cristolla qowan./
 
[V4]
 /Kawsachiway, Señor, munayniykiman jiña./
 Ay, /qori llajtaykiman Qanwan ripusaj./
 
</lyrics></song>